data.description: If you are looking for space this is the place for you. A gorgeous brick ranch on a corner lot with .55 acres. The open living area is bright and cheery with huge windows, a wood burning fireplace, dining area and LVP flooring. Three bedrooms and a newly remodeled bathroom and kitchen make this a very inviting space. You have the option for a private primary bedroom with 1/2 bath and its own entrance or use it as a family room if you choose. The basement is set up for related living with a separate entrance, full kitchen, bedroom, dining room and 3/4 bath. The outdoor living will be easy and comfortable with a sunroom, additional 4 seasons room, patio, hot tub, three car garage with plenty of parking spaces.
